<h4>Create a story</h4>
<p>[ins] with a story selected</p>
<p>right click story &gt; insert after or child</p>
<h4>Edit a story</h4>
<p>[enter] with story selected</p>
<p>right click story &gt; edit</p>
<p>double click story</p>
<h4>Delete a story</h4>
<p>[del]</p>
<p>right click story &gt; delete</p>
<h4>Change stack rank</h4>
<p>Drag story to 3px dropzone between stories</p>
<h4>Change parent</h4>
<p>Drag story into another story</p>
